main event: A civilian reported observing a UFO in Denver, Colorado for 25 minutes on August 23, 1952.
interesting points: The object was reported to be moving southwest at a slow speed before disappearing,It met all conditions of an aircraft sighting but was observed for too long at too slow a speed,Weather conditions were clear with a visibility of 25 miles,The report indicated that while physical evidence was noted, it was not detailed in the document,The sighting was recorded during the Project Blue Book investigation.
